&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /> <img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1707\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/06/DSC00121-scaled.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/06/DSC00121-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;quality=75 2560w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/06/DSC00121-scaled.jpg?resize=1024,683&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/06/DSC00121-scaled.jpg?resize=2000,1333&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/06/DSC00121-scaled.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/06/DSC00121-scaled.jpg?resize=1800,1200&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/06/DSC00121-scaled.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/06/DSC00121-scaled.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/06/DSC00121-scaled.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/06/DSC00121-scaled.jpg?resize=2048,1365&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p>The Lost Sierra is my happy place. I am at home in the endless mountain expanse, loving every moment of the weekend. Covering this race by bike was a treat, and not something I have done in years. Thanks to The Radavist for making space to share the stoke. Lost and Found, The Downieville Classic and a whole season of wonderful riding is made possible by the tireless and often thankless work of the SBTS. If you have it in your heart or your wallet to lend a hand, it would be met with appreciation. These open spaces, cleared and maintained by the stewardship are precious and deserve our collective support and attention. Come and play. The water is warm (ish).</p>\n<p><em>The Builder’s Bazaar included bikes from: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/pinecycles/?hl=en\" target=\"_blank\">Pine Cycles</a>, <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/mosaiccycles/?hl=en\" target=\"_blank\">Mosaic Cycles</a>, <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/seekeradv/?hl=en\" target=\"_blank\">Seeker</a>, <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/breadwinnercycles/?hl=en\" target=\"_blank\">Breadwinner</a>, <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/caletticycles/?hl=en\" target=\"_blank\">Caletti Cycles,</a> <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/bluecollarbikes916/?hl=en\" target=\"_blank\">Blue Collar</a>, <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/coffeeandeggs/?hl=en\" target=\"_blank\">Falconer</a>, <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/manzanitacycles/?hl=en\" target=\"_blank\">Manzanita</a>, <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/prandus_bicycle/?hl=en\" target=\"_blank\">Prandus</a>, <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/squidbikes/?hl=en\" target=\"_blank\">Squid Bikes</a>, <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/sycipdesigns/?hl=en\" target=\"_blank\">Sycip</a>, and <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/mootscycles/?hl=en\" target=\"_blank\">Moots</a>. </em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/lost-and-found-gravel-race-2023/\">100-Mile Love Song: The 2023 Lost &amp; Found Gravel Festival</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"Hailey Moore","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"cd2584304e5f48499038976955a24b4f5bbeff51294259528f445e68a8b9906f","category":"Cycling"}